title: 10 facts about Bratislava you did not know
itunes:author: The Slovak Spectator
itunes:summary:
Anna and Peter will reveal where you can find the oldest Bratislava cinema and introduce you to a few forgotten Bratislava greats, including the iconic Schöne Náci. The latter even has something in common with one of the most successful US rappers. 
 
Photo: TASR 
Source: Po stopách dávnej Bratislavy by V. Tomčík
